text: Could you someone help me for custom code for blog search module ?

Hey can I get some help from HubSpot support? I am working on an app and when I run 'hs project upload' in the CLI it says I don't have access to the beta. It gives me a link to request access, but I follow the link and it shows that I am opted into the beta.

```[ERROR] Couldn't create a React extension with your file `/app/extensions/ExampleCard.jsx` because you don't have access to this beta. To learn more and sign up for the beta, visit <https://app.HubSpot.com/l/whats-new/all?update=13899236>```
